data.description:
Welcome home to 18101 Petworth Circle in the sought after Westfields community! Why wait for new construction when you can own this beautiful home built just last year! 
This sunny colonial has 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Gleaming hardwoods on the main floor take you past the large home office to the open kitchen and bright living room with lots of natural light. The updated kitchen features plenty of counter space and a large island for dining and entertaining. Access the brand new, maintenance free deck with open views of the trees.
Upstairs is large primary bedroom with luxury bath. Two more big bedrooms and an additional full bath.
Upstairs laundry room! Lower level features a large area waiting for your finishing plans and includes a bathroom rough-in. Walkout French doors to the large open backyard backing to trees. Westfields community offers a great location close to shops, restaurants, and an elementary school. Close to I70 and easy commuting.
